to leave the philippines saying otherwise they would face 
drastic action 
assistant press secretary horacio paredes confirmed that 
presidential guards conducted an exercise on those days but refused 
to say if british instructors took part the british embassy was 
closed saturday for the easter holidays 
the young officers union is believed to be an offshoot of the 
reform the armed forces movement which has recently taken the name 
revolutionary alliance for the masses 
both groups claim mrs aquinos government is incompetent and 
corrupt mrs aquino says the rebels simply want to grab power from 
her elected administration which came to power after the 1986 
popular revolt that ousted president ferdinand marcos 
