saying at this time my deep concern is for his family and also 
in participating to create a most adequate and proper tribute for 
this great american 
sparkys death is an enormous loss for the united states and 
people of hawaii he was a great american a peacemaker he was 
distinguished militarily politically socially and globally ill 
remember sparky as having a human local hawaiian touch when it 
came to politics 
carolyn tanaka press secretary to waihee said it would be 
